DWFFDefinedObjectPropertyVisitor Class Reference
[DWF Publisher API]

#include "dwf/publisher/impl/DefinedObjectPropertyVisitor.h"

Detailed Description

An implementation for objects (visitors) that publishers can use with publishable sources to extract their property data. This implementation is used for working with defined objects for DWF toolkit version 7.1. This class should be used in conjuction with the DWFPublishedDefinedObjectVisitor.

Since:
7.2.0
